":"19","parent":"16","text":"• Requiere drenaje pleural o cirugía (1,2,3,4).","guid":"0F8FWW7J-0Y0oSk0We0B5A","children":[]}]},{"id":"20","parent":"13","text":"• Empiema:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"21","parent":"20","text":"• Colección de pus franco en el espacio pleural (1).","guid":"xoWTg0Ia9u6PEFr38OGr4w","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"22","parent":"0","text":"Clasificación de Light de Derrames\\NParaneumónicos y Empiema","guid":"YwwBu1S1sTss-Nz6Wwq4fA","children":[{"id":"23","parent":"22","text":"Clase 1 - Derrame\\Nparaneumónico no significativo:","guid":"-QjSPk1nb-gzUWrROEndxg","children":[{"id":"24","parent":"23","text":"• < 10 mm en radiografía\\Nen decúbito","guid":"QWaaD0_0ARDBvgiFJjo0rA","children":[]}]},{"id":"25","parent":"22","text":"Clase 2 - Derrame\\Nparaneumónico típico:","guid":"IkkZP57KJTnjz0AGckT1Yw","children":[{"id":"26","parent":"25","text":"•  10 mm en radiografía en decúbito","guid":"Z3_OCyvDO-4Jhs6v2QTvSA","children":[]},{"id":"27","parent":"25","text":"• Glucosa > 40 mg/dL","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"28","parent":"25","text":"• pH > 7.2","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"29","parent":"25","text":"• Tinción de Gram y cultivo negativos","guid":"SaHofZ1XbzcQ5BD9MqPLNw","children":[]}]},{"id":"30","parent":"22","text":"Clase 3 - Derrame paraneumónico\\Nborderline complicado:","guid":"e4dlc_TWlTlNQnLzFuLK7g","children":[{"id":"31","parent":"30","text":"• pH 7-7.2 y/o LDH > 1000 U/L y glucosa > 40 mg/dL","guid":"szmrwsbVwtJU6QYMk2efoQ","children":[]},{"id":"32","parent":"30","text":"• Tinción de Gram y cultivo negativos","guid":"IUJER0D7QKaeB9wEbAcSvQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"33","parent":"22","text":"Clase 4 - Derrame\\Nparaneumónico simple\\Ncomplicado:","guid":"ILijQs4oq_9vBu8r4uTu1Q","children":[{"id":"34","parent":"33","text":"• pH < 7 y/o glucosa < 40 mg/dL y/o tinción de Gram o cultivo positivo","guid":"Kg4n84xvyKvAprW2isOoyw","children":[]},{"id":"35","parent":"33","text":"• No loculado","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"36","parent":"33","text":"• No pus franco","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"37","parent":"22","text":"Clase 5 - Derrame paraneumónico\\Ncomplejo complicado:","guid":"H77b082uiSZkx11pZc4eYA","children":[{"id":"38","parent":"37","text":"• pH < 7 y/o glucosa < 40 mg/dL y/o tinción de Gram o cultivo positivo","guid":"xqGVhVHU4B2DYbF9i1Srpw","children":[]},{"id":"39","parent":"37","text":"• Multiloculado","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"40","parent":"22","text":"Clase 6 - Empiema\\Nsimple:","guid":"6O1y9HHw9NA49dOYyDbymQ","children":[{"id":"41","parent":"40","text":"• Pus franco","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"42","parent":"40","text":"• Loculación única o flujo libre","guid":"gGP0VHx1h3cymsu9YdOnvg","children":[]}]},{"id":"43","parent":"22","text":"Clase 7 - Empiema\\Ncomplejo:","guid":"mxz0PWS7YkBvUzqM0N12Bw","children":[{"id":"44","parent":"43","text":"• Pus franco","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"45","parent":"43","text":"• Multiloculado","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"46","parent":"0","text":"Epidemiología del Derrame\\NParaneumónico y Empiema","guid":"kwoNqCwclBI8NIt-2lF-Zg","children":[{"id":"47","parent":"46","text":"Incidencia/Prevalencia:","guid":"7vr5LnFt7vSfdwQz8P2bIg","children":[{"id":"48","parent":"47","text":"• El derrame paraneumónico complica aproximadamente\\Nel 20%-57% de los casos de neumonía (4).","guid":"Cfb_Eel8z2zVYO-jxRgzEg","children":[]},{"id":"49","parent":"47","text":"• Hasta el 40% de los derrames paraneumónicos pueden\\Ninfectarse (complicado) o convertirse en empiema (4).","guid":"UWhN1RNNTNKGPdmeazukPQ","children":[]},{"id":"50","parent":"47","text":"• Los derrames paraneumónicos son más\\Ncomunes en niños y ancianos (2).","guid":"VI3t4VPSE-ZwNntOSop8gQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"51","parent":"46","text":"Resumen de Estudio:","guid":"YXbacKrOOkm_LQw1XinmNw","children":[{"id":"52","parent":"51","text":"• Incidencia anual del empiema\\Nparaneumónico en EE.UU.:","guid":"tqZYy4WPRQQKZVPYrnJemw","children":[{"id":"53","parent":"52","text":"• Aumentó de 3.04 a 5.98 por 100,\\N000 personas de 1996 a 2008\\N(Thorax 2011 Aug;66(8):663).","guid":"bocFsKGnDLTZjhGVFIpgfg","children":[]},{"id":"54","parent":"52","text":"• Basado en un estudio de\\Ncohorte retrospectivo.","guid":"U89R6THXwcM7t5KlfTx45A","children":[{"id":"55","parent":"54","text":"• Datos de alta del National Inpatient\\NSample entre 1996 y 2008.","guid":"sFCIqqukzer34Y4vtVpnHA","children":[]},{"id":"56","parent":"54","text":"• 157,094 hospitalizaciones\\Nestimadas relacionadas con\\Nempiema paraneumónico.","guid":"qBribvbo0LhILLPTWnykHw","children":[]},{"id":"57","parent":"54","text":"• Tasas de hospitalización por\\Nempiema paraneumónico:","guid":"i0n6nUAiYyRDAgcIIwMdiA","children":[{"id":"58","parent":"57","text":"• 3.04 por 100,\\N000 en 1996.","guid":"7PAuRUikBBKXJgGz404NXg","children":[]},{"id":"59","parent":"57","text":"• 5.98 por 100,\\N000 en 2008.","guid":"gXCtbCuDD02zlHGIiCDE0A","children":[]},{"id":"60","parent":"57","text":"• RR de incidencia 2\\N(95% CI 1.8-2.1).","guid":"p6c1KYC5zuEBl5Ol-M4F3Q","children":[]}]},{"id":"61","parent":"54","text":"• Tasas de hospitalización por empiema\\Nparaneumónico por edad:","guid":"wcbIdKjCdv5v37zuQlWqpA","children":[{"id":"62","parent":"61","text":"• Niños ≤ 18 años:","guid":"9d5cSexOPj2e8MdSC4oehg","children":[{"id":"63","parent":"62","text":"• Incidencia media anual 2.76 por\\N100,000 (95% CI 2.49-3.07).","guid":"fuYtr8LdnCyzbPoENVO9Yg","children":[]},{"id":"64","parent":"62","text":"• RR de incidencia comparando 1996 con\\N2008, 1.9 (95% CI 1.4-2.7).","guid":"NJD9bXOrbuYbXa0KRWTqeA","children":[]}]},{"id":"65","parent":"61","text":"• Adultos de 18-39 años:","guid":"n_wuOOv4qPtDbnRRGGyV4g","children":[{"id":"66","parent":"65","text":"• Incidencia media anual 1.89 por\\N100,000 (95% CI 1.82-1.97).","guid":"dYO_NJ3WZJKkvLKMoCDFqg","children":[]},{"id":"67","parent":"65","text":"• RR de incidencia comparando 1996 con\\N2008, 1.8 (95% CI 1.5-2.1).","guid":"ixjixNqVcdIfrPXQmZN45Q","children":[]}]},{"id":"