 adquiridas en el hospital:","guid":"MFyve7MDBN_1xyAiXChOxA","children":[{"id":"137","parent":"136","text":"• Staphylococcus aureus resistente a meticilina (MRSA): ~25%","guid":"aZ-SYKYH12Op1D_Xco75VA","children":[]},{"id":"138","parent":"136","text":"• Staphylococcus aureus sensible a meticilina (MSSA): ~10%","guid":"OhrN-BeAY0XyY_xHHw06tQ","children":[]},{"id":"139","parent":"136","text":"• Aerobios Gram-negativos, incluyendo E. coli, Pseudomonas aeruginosa y Klebsiella spp.: 23%","guid":"jxh_Pb8rdBEE4MU8nl_T1g","children":[]},{"id":"140","parent":"136","text":"• Streptococcus spp.: 18%","guid":"q_dtwpV8NPn5pw3wO95TsA","children":[]},{"id":"141","parent":"136","text":"• Enterococos: ~12%","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"142","parent":"136","text":"• Anaerobios: 8%","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"143","parent":"136","text":"• Patógenos atípicos (Legionella spp., Mycoplasma spp.): Raros","guid":"33qv49J14P5l4lAM4t24pw","children":[]}]},{"id":"144","parent":"128","text":"Factores adicionales\\Ndel paciente:","guid":"4YmN-g7bOd3yPfAYiJ4t9A","children":[{"id":"145","parent":"144","text":"• Edad","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"146","parent":"144","text":"• Localización geográfica","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"147","parent":"144","text":"• Comorbilidades","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"148","parent":"144","text":"• Flora orofaríngea (2)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"149","parent":"128","text":"Resumen de\\NEstudios:","guid":"i4R8ZXeb4lfWzVPnQybPqA","children":[{"id":"150","parent":"149","text":"1. Revisión Sistemática:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"151","parent":"150","text":"• Organismo más común en infecciones pleurales\\Nbacterianas en adultos: Staphylococcus aureus","guid":"eBoLrY4Ga7TS9IVPqNWRvA","children":[]},{"id":"152","parent":"150","text":"• Microbiología de la infección pleural\\Nbacteriana en 10,241 adultos (2008-2018):","guid":"8GEN1AUKSZPZeUFov7TsXQ","children":[{"id":"153","parent":"152","text":"• 6,202 aislados bacterianos identificados","guid":"67sNSEcF0MPxKUh9W54gXA","children":[]},{"id":"154","parent":"152","text":"• Bacterias aerobias Gram-positivas: 50.4% (95% CI 48%-50.6%)","guid":"jwBh2BowD8lUcuGRv-DsWw","children":[]},{"id":"155","parent":"152","text":"• Bacterias aerobias Gram-negativas: 37.5% (95% CI 37.2%-39.6%)","guid":"V38FWjZMzIdbpkfBAxL_iA","children":[]},{"id":"156","parent":"152","text":"• Bacterias anaeróbicas: 12.1% (95% CI 11.4%-13.1%)","guid":"ST-83q0pBAczp4DykawCWA","children":[]},{"id":"157","parent":"152","text":"• Aislados aeróbicos\\Nmás comunes:","guid":"_52rTkAKGkptvPr8dUTG2w","children":[{"id":"158","parent":"157","text":"• S. aureus: 20.7%","guid":"8dhD1RPYeczGklw20HKNig","children":[]},{"id":"159","parent":"157","text":"• Streptococos viridans: 18.7%","guid":"P-PV7gwhZfvTKB7NL8Y6fw","children":[]},{"id":"160","parent":"157","text":"• Pseudomonas spp.: 17.6%","guid":"uCMsltGO9Opoe-l-SR5C5g","children":[]},{"id":"161","parent":"157","text":"• Enterobacteriaceae: 11.9%","guid":"vuTRsknQu_4YNnf15zhl9A","children":[]},{"id":"162","parent":"157","text":"• S. pneumoniae: 10.8%","guid":"gbGCSeDkeER9Sa5fwLLcfA","children":[]},{"id":"163","parent":"157","text":"• Klebsiella spp.: 10.7%","guid":"37039TwMqiEd-M6WXqn72w","children":[]},{"id":"164","parent":"157","text":"• Acinetobacter spp.: 5%","guid":"S-3jo1-N8IipQAjvmXkngw","children":[]},{"id":"165","parent":"157","text":"• Estafilococos coagulasa-negativos: 4. 5%","guid":"F77ZcPYDs3yTjDCDsGHw6g","children":[]}]},{"id":"166","parent":"152","text":"• Variaciones\\Ngeográficas:","guid":"0rEfNIfDplvsUm38jlx5vQ","children":[{"id":"167","parent":"166","text":"• Neumococos: aislado más\\Ncomún en regiones tropicales","guid":"NT7ZGmry-413GZcAn_YPHA","children":[]},{"id":"168","parent":"166","text":"• Streptococos viridans: aislado más\\Ncomún en regiones templadas","guid":"gqUsoo0LEHmjm6-mH51u2g","children":[]},{"id":"169","parent":"166","text":"• Mayor incidencia de infecciones por bacterias\\NGram-negativas en subtrópicos comparado\\Ncon trópicos y regiones templadas (Eur Respir\\NJ 2019 Sep;54(3)).","guid":"opzR5xKapc6i-8bXOecUBQ","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"170","parent":"149","text":"2. Estudio de Cohorte\\N(1999-2012):","guid":"DW65MX3Jj3dakSpPM9kuSA","children":[{"id":"171","parent":"170","text":"• 406 pacientes con\\Nempiema revisados","guid":"poWoz5Wkmt5006_R2V7C6g","children":[]},{"id":"172","parent":"170","text":"• Identificación del organismo infeccioso\\Nen 56.4% de los pacientes","guid":"i3uGgy4Gxk76_ycjj9EjOQ","children":[{"id":"173","parent":"172","text":"• Estreptococos: 19.5%","guid":"lFUIkoRbVo06AOozwd_KgQ","children":[]},{"id":"174","parent":"172","text":"• S. pneumoniae: 9.6%","guid":"6d2TKh0nH7EXoNp6K-fY1Q","children":[]},{"id":"175","parent":"172","text":"• Streptococcus\\Nmilleri: 4.2%","guid":"SC0FOZMR42BHtyV0gpdDNQ","children":[]},{"id":"176","parent":"172","text":"• Estafilococos: 15.5%","guid":"yjLpjeqkrQLv_pfIc_p-MQ","children":[]},{"id":"177","parent":"172","text":"• MSSA: 8.9%","guid":"qR2PiJ0nhu7dWbYI2GFSkg","children":[]},{"id":"178","parent":"172","text":"• MRSA: 6.7%","guid":"qbSglVX89NQmVKV67vaCRQ","children":[]},{"id":"179","parent":"172","text":"• Bacilos\\NGram-negativos:\\N10.1%","guid":"61GY66EGZVRl-MxHTeWBOA","children":[]},{"id":"180","parent":"172","text":"•\\NEnterobacteriaceae:\\N5.7%","guid":"dyqcJpuyQR4m5zqGwz5ngQ","children":[]},{"id":"181","parent":"172","text":"• P. aeruginosa: 4.4%","guid":"cRGWwY2TB9FSpnWuHPkd7g","children":[]},{"id":"182","parent":"172","text":"• Micobacterias: 9.1%","guid":"3MG2DylxtuDvAMFwzwsbEQ","children":[]},{"id":"183","parent":"172","text":"• Anaerobios: 5.7%","guid":"E7sVA3rb2IsgAEorlKJmEw","children":[]},{"id":"184","parent":"172","text":"• Hongos: 2.2%","guid":"Mz825pL9FKOCppxZqJCW1w","children":[]},{"id":"185","parent":"172","text":"• Infección polimicrobiana: 8.4%\\N(PLoS One 2012;7(1):e30074).","guid":"mlBd9PtpSFznw0bByCPVVA","children":[]}]}]}]}]},{"id":"186","parent":"0","text":"Patogénesis del Derrame\\NParaneumónico y Empiema","guid":"2jObdcd9PATlp8LB4Km0wQ","children":[{"id":"187","parent":"186","text":"Balance de Secreción y\\NAbsorción de Líquido Pleural:","guid":"koypu2IjZVnUunh9KEtmKw","children":[{"id":"188","parent":"187","text":"• Desequilibrio → acumulación de\\Nlíquido en espacio pleural (3).","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"189","parent":"186","text":"Derrame Pleural\\NTransudativo:","guid":"wHVOFDL3HWpNhuqaMby3AQ","children":[{"id":"190","parent":"189","text":"• Migración de líquido a través de capilares intactos","guid":"1ng7Ic3Zqhbjo9NKizWwAQ","children":[]},{"id":"191","parent":"189","text":"• Causas: insuficiencia cardíaca, cirrosis hepática","guid":"6zC-gkSyfq2zvvNRUtcIEQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"192","parent":"186","text":"Derrame Pleural\\NExudativo:","guid":"iglivC6KUimu47OWpldymg","children":[{"id":"193","parent":"192","text":"• Migración de líquido a través de capilares dilatados","guid":"BcPM9ocKm4Ut8JXtpF4cOw","children":[]},{"id":"194","parent":"192","text":"• Causas: neumonía, malignidad pleural, embolia pulmonar, enfermedad gastrointestinal","guid":"0VxK0z5Wth2F0lGGtzC6BQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"195","parent":"186","text":"Derrames\\NParaneumónicos:","guid":"nSzfr0Sz7j6LSFj4ghDEEw","children":[{"id":"196","parent":"195","text":"• Exudativos","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"197","parent":"195","text":"• Resultado de neumonía bacteriana, absceso pulmonar, bronquiectasias","guid":"W7d5N-aPKEhHDZEwpjL05Q","children":[]}]},{"id":"198","parent":"186","text":"Infección del Derrame Paraneumónico\\N→ Empiema (2,3, 4):","guid":"DJ1Skabfg5sD76nJDVgyUg","children":[{"id":"199","parent":"198","text":"1. Fase Inicial:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"200","parent":"199","text":"• Comienza como derrame exudativo estéril","guid":"4lFi7AoEgjEqIg3rQYGyAg","children":[]},{"id":"201","parent":"199","text":"• Neutrófilos y monocitos atraviesan la capa mesotelial pleural → espacio pleural","guid":"lLZz5ZD0zNWuB4a8sMAuqA","children":[]},{"id":"202","parent":"199","text":"• ↑ Citoquinas inflamatorias (IL-6, IL-8, TNF-α)","guid":"dujnh5LRMrH93Gl87sr2Dg","children":[]},{"id":"203","parent":"199","text":"• ↑ Permeabilidad vascular → derrame pleural estéril","guid":"Va7VuCZSqiY1IRLrtSJbbg","children":[]}]},{"id":"204","parent":"198","text":"2. Fase\\NFibrinopurulenta\\NTransicional:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"205","parent":"204","text":"• Infección del derrame exudativo","guid":"la8gLPsmSLoLfMfSTsGoHg","children":[]},{"id":"206","parent":"204","text":"• ↑ Permeabilidad vascular → migración microbiana al espacio pleural","guid":"FBnBCV4UvUwhxE2TJHJ7qQ","children":[]},{"id":"207","parent":"204","text":"• ↑ Inhibidor del activador del plasminógeno, ↓ activador tisular del plasminógeno","guid":"NOARKrpPl6mx_9bPMsGt9w","children":[]},{"id":"208","parent":"204","text":"• ↓ Glucosa, ↓ pH, ↑ ácido láctico, ↑ CO2 en líquido pleural","guid":"p1JdlTc94oAEYr1JP3k9TQ","children":[]},{"id":"209","parent":"204","text":"• Desarrollo de loculaciones","guid":"3xkv8NojgH8Yww4k2YK52Q","children":[]},{"id":"210","parent":"204","text":"• Purulencia → empiema","guid":"t09wEtnI-lH3aWp5qx2_PA","children":[]}]},{"id":"211","parent":"198","text":"3. Fase Crónica u\\NOrganizativa:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"212","parent":"211","text":"• Proliferación de fibroblastos","guid":"FGRFzIorxEdMyYfRnr_gnQ","children":[]},{"id":"213","parent":"211","text":"• Producción y depósito de fibrina en espacio pleural","guid":"W3yqujUOWUSjrpCvsIOCwA","children":[]},{"id":"214","parent":"211","text":"• Formación de septaciones","guid":"DH_Avh0V2ksc_gtY--8Xsg","children":[]},{"id":"215","parent":"211","text":"• Engrosamiento de membranas intrapleurales, pérdida de elasticidad","guid":"cn7XuHkSLtumav6UYp6WRA","children":[]},{"id":"216","parent":"211","text":"• Producción de una capa pleural → impide reexpansión pulmonar","guid":"yT6vG5nnsPKv7UdfnHHjGA","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"217","parent":"0","text":"Historia\\NClínica","guid":"MGEfTcygu0LP1hSc7hU9_A","children":[{"id":"218","parent":"217","text":"Motivo de\\NConsulta (CC):","guid":"K67xt9h6wqwsilWOVpDkcg","children":[{"id":"219","parent":"218","text":"• Síntomas iniciales del derrame\\Nparaneumónico similares a neumonía (3,4):","guid":"uQLiGprHBIycIc11K_C7Vw","children":[{"id":"220","parent":"219","text":"• Dolor torácico sordo o pleurítico","guid":"wOlYCI0SOIkq7EINn46H9Q","children":[]},{"id":"221","parent":"219","text":"• Disnea","guid":"F15-GyTYavVjCeLjcrpFrw","children":[]},{"id":"222","parent":"219","text":"• Tos","guid":"LKZKQgOtSlqz984gIowvbQ","children":[]},{"id":"223","parent":"219","text":"• Fiebre y escalofríos","guid":"Fiv8JMT9mkUKdNtuSajCHQ","children":[]},{"id":"224","parent":"219","text":"• Producción de esputo","guid":"i-Ub8WZ2eT2p9Ux91CcJqg","children":[]},{"id":"225","parent":"219","text":"• Pérdida de peso","guid":"MCNPk1NAK2fwPcv2tgCYXw","children":[]}]},{"id":"226","parent":"218","text":"• Empiema anaeróbico puede ser más\\Nindolente y presentar (4):","guid":"","children":[{"id":"227","parent":"226","text":"• Pérdida de peso","guid":"6kfTygv9CqdHkZQR9tOv8A","children":[]},{"id":"228","parent":"226","text":"• Anorexia","guid":"w2tl-pM6BMbeSXxevKERJQ","children":[]},{"id":"229","parent":"226","text":"• Malestar general","guid":"lvsCwwWc0kCo0B3qOC7MmA","children":[]}]},{"id":"230","parent":"218","text":"• Si el derrame no se drena, el curso puede\\Nser fulminante con presentación de (3,4):","guid":"MHdi-3O5M5BH0a_IJTmrUw","children":[{"id":"231","parent":"230","text":"• Sepsis","guid":"OiKDAADI_P9Rhsrq1Zb7_A","children":[]},{"id":"232","parent":"230","text":"• Taponamiento cardíaco\\N(debido a gran colección en espacio pleural)","guid":"FeGOgmvxkeyD4qh61hioHQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"233","parent":"218","text":"Resumen\\Nde Estudio:","guid":"6gKnVqhTo9VPXwBbD3AUKw","children":[{"id":"234","parent":"233","text":"• Empiema adquirido en hogar de ancianos\\Nvs. adquirido en la comunidad:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"235","parent":"234","text":"• Estudio de cohorte: J Am Geriatr Soc 2007 Nov;55(11):1847","guid":"AUQ7csv5ZY65vVq1iq-weA","children":[]},{"id":"236","parent":"234","text":"• 144 pacientes admitidos de la comunidad y 55 transferidos de hogar de ancianos con empiema","guid":"Hii9z63K4rCzyyBwmf5nIg","children":[]},{"id":"237","parent":"234","text":"• Empiema adquirido en la comunidad → presentación más aguda con fiebre, tos y dolor torácico","guid":"r0Dz52mHU3r92wsMx3blOw","children":[]},{"id":"238","parent":"234","text":"• Empiema adquirido en hogar de ancianos → presentación más retrasada con disnea, pérdida de peso y anemia (p < 0.05)","guid":"E_XfW5E00qePqruoAFDZTQ","children":[]},{"id":"239","parent":"234","text":"• Organismos anaeróbicos más comúnmente aislados en pacientes de hogar de ancianos","guid":"S8O-FOIuMAfG1Q5GwV9lUA","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"240","parent":"217","text":"Historia de la\\NEnfermedad Actual\\N(HPI):","guid":"NN2TlPjOeyw6IWhl_G6OMA","children":[{"id":"241","parent":"240","text":"• Preguntar sobre indicadores de neumonía\\Nno respondedora, incluyendo (2,4):","guid":"0lpxyUPbDxOFjTt63AAu1Q","children":[{"id":"242","parent":"241","text":"• Diagnóstico reciente de neumonía","guid":"va3C3Y0s2B1w1Ha5DcLSEg","children":[]},{"id":"243","parent":"241","text":"• Tiempo de inicio de los síntomas","guid":"-XrDpBpVFaq18jKd3BE0hw","children":[]},{"id":"244","parent":"241","text":"• Fiebre persistente","guid":"u3esutaKnzL1d2IJ8O3i0w","children":[]},{"id":"245","parent":"241","text":"• Uso de antibióticos","guid":"3fmdkeCQHBzGRt9UqndyHg","children":[]},{"id":"246","parent":"241","text":"• Pérdida de peso o fiebre","guid":"i-7ADbGjbYj1NZM0y7u2Yg","children":[]}]},{"id":"247","parent":"240","text":"• Preguntar sobre factores de riesgo para\\Nempiema, incluyendo (2,4):","guid":"","children":[{"id":"248","parent":"247","text":"• Inmunocompromiso (uso de corticosteroides, infección por VIH, diabetes mellitus)","guid":"qAAVDo4-_OHWeTyWWGGlGA","children":[]},{"id":"249","parent":"247","text":"• Abuso de alcohol o drogas","guid":"KwqW1pwOQk6DGef1hkwKtA","children":[]},{"id":"250","parent":"247","text":"• Cirugía torácica, procedimientos o trauma recientes","guid":"iZZm1ArUumjq_XiokU8Rqw","children":[]},{"id":"251","parent":"247","text":"• Condiciones que predispongan a infección anaeróbica (aspiración, mala dentición)","guid":"5Qf_kHgYEU0dUuA5cpYJ-Q","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"252","parent":"217","text":"Historia de\\NMedicamentos:","guid":"DVe7SOHcLPB5889Ledm6Mg","children":[{"id":"253","parent":"252","text":"• Revisar medicamentos, ya que muchos pueden causar derrame pleural\\Nexudativo; el culpable más común es inhibidores de la tirosina quinasa (1).","guid":"FVd53wFazysCIoEh30QwWw","children":[]}]},{"id":"254","parent":"217","text":"Historia\\NSocial:","guid":"r0oj21_x2-ibTG9Wgq1MFg","children":[{"id":"255","parent":"254","text":"• Preguntar sobre historia ocupacional y exposición previa a asbesto (1).","guid":"8Z7d2pPm6xzE8Uz7G1ThSw","children":[]},{"id":"256","parent":"254","text":"• Preguntar sobre factores sociales asociados\\Ncon tuberculosis (TB), incluyendo (1):","guid":"VlxG3P2g6RbFHS4gNEZ8EA","children":[{"id":"257","parent":"256","text":"• Vivir con o exposición a persona con TB","guid":"uiomVnL8yA_Y7S6wEM3QbQ","children":[]},{"id":"258","parent":"256","text":"• Vivir en o viajar a áreas con alta tasa de TB","guid":"Ddi65C6XDv-enQU-UbPl-Q","children":[]},{"id":"259","parent":"256","text":"• Situación de calle","guid":"20QY9EhgZcgwaxkZzxUDfg","children":[]},{"id":"260","parent":"256","text":"• Encarcelamiento","guid":"1PhXMg9d25u8tjtiFnBJeA","children":[]},{"id":"261","parent":"256","text":"• Desnutrición","guid":"8YzAWdVteHWXw9hevLlZ8Q","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"262","parent":"217","text":"Referencias:","guid":"VaddYFAoKzaUEpRsTFQsmQ","children":[{"id":"263","parent":"262","text":"1. [Referencia 1]","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"264","parent":"262","text":"2. [Referencia 2]","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"265","parent":"262","text":"3. [Referencia 3]","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"266","parent":"262","text":"4. [Referencia 4]","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"267","parent":"0","text":"Diagnóstico","guid":"","children":[{"id":"268","parent":"267","text":"Sospechar derrame paraneumónico\\Nen pacientes con:","guid":"zGnddRC3HC-Dp5oV7MRJcQ","children":[{"id":"269","parent":"268","text":"• Neumonía que no responde al tratamiento antibiótico en 72 horas, especialmente si presentan:","guid":"h4RFrgslf_4gwB6LqVyJPQ","children":[]},{"id":"270","parent":"268","text":"• Fiebre persistente","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"271","parent":"268","text":"• Leucocitosis persistente","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"272","parent":"268","text":"• Proteína C reactiva elevada","guid":"SnvXbTqbn6iwgP-9e0Sb6g","children":[]},{"id":"273","parent":"268","text":"• Fiebre, tos, disnea y dolor torácico pleurítico","guid":"DDjmxlq4dY9NtTAClVKIbg","children":[]},{"id":"274","parent":"268","text":"• Hipoxemia, frote pleural, disminución de ruidos respiratorios y frémito","guid":"0Q_yWr4ExJ6g1FB3GqRrGw","children":[]},{"id":"275","parent":"268","text":"• Opacidades progresivas, dependientes de la gravedad, basadas\\Nen la pleura y que oscurecen el diafragma en las imágenes","guid":"cmZvb8G-hUQ-uVupwlUlRQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"276","parent":"267","text":"Considerar\\Ntoracocentesis si:","guid":"AHc_yLzfER5LQcKdGDnNJg","children":[{"id":"277","parent":"276","text":"• Las imágenes muestran > 10 mm de líquido en Rx en decúbito lateral o\\N> 20-22 mm en ultrasonido o tomografía computarizada","guid":"mGLrFjjhjMmiRrSs1VeWLQ","children":[]},{"id":"278","parent":"276","text":"• Es seguro proceder (estado respiratorio, hemodinámico y de coagulación adecuado)","guid":"CpjNu2FHPvfONslrRKYTeQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"279","parent":"267","text":"Hallazgos en el líquido pleural\\Nque apoyan un derrame\\Ncomplicado (infectado):","guid":"dL22Tu4L0BNclcb8xDRnyQ","children":[{"id":"280","parent":"279","text":"• pH < 7.2","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"281","parent":"279","text":"• Glucosa < 40 mg/dL (2.22 mmol/L)","guid":"t06Mj53DbLiIoW0VqJFwYA","children":[]},{"id":"282","parent":"279","text":"• Tinción de Gram positiva","guid":"M8zOHv6RU83cGumgxXerhQ","children":[]},{"id":"283","parent":"279","text":"• Líquido purulento","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"284","parent":"267","text":"Criterios de Light (para diferenciar\\Nexudados de transudados):","guid":"YMzhFiwrIgVkOZ8QY5IqUw","children":[{"id":"285","parent":"284","text":"• Exudado: líquido con ≥ 1 de las\\Nsiguientes características:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"286","parent":"285","text":"• Relación de proteína pleural/sérica > 0.5","guid":"lKYmwHzRIU334I9CO8Ze8A","children":[]},{"id":"287","parent":"285","text":"• Relación de LDH pleural/sérico > 0.6","guid":"OmnO07G9M_5YuXaltDW67Q","children":[]},{"id":"288","parent":"285","text":"• LDH pleural > 0.67 veces el límite superior normal de LDH sérica","guid":"WSSsV4c0mCwy9eY-_812hQ","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"289","parent":"0","text":"Sociedad\\NTorácica\\NBritánica:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"290","parent":"289","text":"• Considera un conjunto de evidencia clínica de infección,\\Nlíquido purulento, cultivo positivo o tinción de Gram positiva, y\\NpH del líquido < 7.2 como diagnóstico de derrame\\Nparaneumónico complicado o empiema (1).","guid":"jmk7GUePa4WvsN5xEryQAg","children":[]}]},{"id":"291","parent":"0","text":"Referencias:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"292","parent":"291","text":"1. [Referencia 1]","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"293","parent":"291","text":"2. [Referencia 2]","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"294","parent":"291","text":"3. [Referencia 3]","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"295","parent":"291","text":"4. [Referencia 4]","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},"node_count":295,"relations":[],"cross_references":[],"specialty":"Neumología","folder":"Entidades clínicas/Neumología","filename":"Empiema-2024","id":"map_1354","resolved_references":[]}